<para style="p">

  <verse number="17" style="v" />We were separated from you, brothers, for a short time, in person not in heart. We were especially eager, with great desire, to see your face.

  <verse number="18" style="v" />For we wished to come to you, I, Paul, once and again, but Satan stopped us.

  <verse number="19" style="v" />For what is our confidence for the future, or joy, or crown of pride in front of our Lord Jesus at his coming? Is it not you just as much as others?

  <verse number="20" style="v" />For you are our glory and our joy.</para>
